column2: "Hey, listen... Back on Naberius during that last exam quest..."
"Yeah, I was there, too. It was unreal how many Darkers there were."
"The thing is, in the middle of a bunch of Darkers, I saw a girl."
"Even the dude that was with me didn't believe me, but I really did see someone!"
"It really looked like a girl was there."
"Maybe it was just a dream... No, I'm sure I saw it..."
"She was there, but I wasn't able to do anything about it..."
